  "description": {
    "zh": "注意脚下！哈哈开个玩笑。当这些混蛋进入那个集装箱时不会有任何警告，只会有一声“轰”！问题解决了。听起来很棒，不是吗？\n这个计划是万无一失的！如果你怀疑，我们可以打赌，但我了解你，你永远不会怀疑我，这就是我喜欢你的地方，我的哥们！\n\n现在我们来谈谈你这部分的任务，我付钱给几个当地匪徒去稍微激怒一下这些猎犬，嘲讽他们之类的，不管用什么方法让这些竞技场的家伙生气。我希望他们发现他们宝贵的货物现在不见了，他们只有一种方法能发现！他们得检查超级秘密的藏匿点——既然已经被发现了，也就不那么秘密了。\n\n不过要赶快设置好诡雷，他们可能已经在路上了，坏人可不会等你，我的哥们。",
    "en": "Watch your step! Haha just kidding. There won't be any warnings when these fuckers enter that container, there will only be a \"boom\"! Problem solved. Sounds great, doesn't it?\nThis plan is fool-proof! We can bet if you doubt it but I know you, you wouldn't doubt me ever, and that's what I love about you my guy!\n\nNow let's talk about your part of this task, I paid a few local bandits to piss off these hounds a little, taunt them and shit, whatever it takes to make these arena fellows angry. I hope they figure out that their valuable cargo is gone now, only one way for them to find out! They gotta check the super secret hiding place - Which isn't so secret anymore since it got busted.\n\nHurry up with setting up the booby-traps tho, they might already be on their way, bad guys don't wait for you my man."
  },
